<hl>
<seg id=1> Shantou New and High Technology Developing Zone Draws Attention of Domestic and Foreign Investors. </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Shantou, December 20 - Due to the improvement of investment environment and a good developing tendency, Shantou New and High Technology Developing Zone draws attention of domestic and foreign investors. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Some Chaozhou scientists who reside in "Silicon Valley" in U.S. expressed their wish to establish new and high technology industry in the zone; the president of Motorola China, the relative personnel of Ericsson company also came to the developing zone to negotiate on the investment projects; while the businessmen from Taiwan expressed their intention to establish science and technologt software R & D companies in the developing zone. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> At present, Shantou New and High Technology Developing Zone has already had accumulative investment of 1.8 billion yuan, constructed factory buildings of 370,000 square meters, the infrastructures and supporting facilities like water, electricity, communication, and bounded warehouse etc have been built and put into operation. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> Up to the beginning of November this year, totally 177 projects were set up in the zone with an overall investment of 6.4 billion yuan including 50% foreign investment. Among the projects in this zone, seven enterprises were recognized as State new and high technology enterprise. </seg>
<seg id=6> In this year, the accumulative industrial output in this zone registered 3.7 billion yuan, total income from technology, industry, and trade reached 4.55 billion yuan, export volume was 127.47 million US dollars, achieved tax and profit of 360 million yuan. </seg>
<seg id=7> Meanwhile, Shantou municipality made and released more than 10 regulations, policies, and measures to encourage the establishment of knowledge-intensive and technology-intensive industries with new and high technology in this zone. </seg>
</p>
